    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>42932,43016,43356,43500,43632</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Mel&gt;</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>&lt;Mel&gt;</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Speakers>
  <Strings>
    <Section>Main</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>42796</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_003_111_000&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>オレ、もっと大冒険したかったな、
命を懸けて世界を救うようなさ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>This sure has been one big adventure. I never thought we'd put our lives on the line to save the world!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>42936</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_003_111_001&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>したじゃない、大冒険。時間を行ったり来たりして
&lt;Cless&gt;さんや&lt;Mint&gt;さん、&lt;Chester&gt;さんたちと</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>It really has been a great adventure. We travelled through time and met all sorts of people like Mister &lt;Cless&gt;, Miss &lt;Mint&gt;, and Mister &lt;Chester&gt;.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43020</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_003_111_002&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>わたしには全部、命懸けだったよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>All the way through giving the best we got.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43092</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_003_111_003&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そうだよな……うん</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Yeah, that's right.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43192</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_003_111_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>この旅で世界が救われるとか
そんなんじゃないけど</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Though this whole journey wasn't about saving the world.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43292</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_003_111_005&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>オレら、自分の結論出すために
ここまで来たんだ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>It was about giving us the chance to find our answer.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43360</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_003_111_006&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>悲しい結論だけど</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>It's a sad conclusion, though...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43428</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_003_111_007&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>後悔してんのか</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>With a bit of regret, yeah.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43504</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_003_111_008&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>してるよ、ちょっとだけ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Maybe, but just a little bit.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43636</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_003_111_009&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>でも、これが逃げずに向き合った結果。
自分のやったことに対する相応の決着だから</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>But all of this started from running away. It's time we face our problems head on.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43708</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_003_111_010&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>オレも……おんなじだ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I feel the same...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
</SceneText>
